des: Ask Alexa for your Mystic Keeper's horoscopes any time, and she'll read a randomly-selected responses. You can ask for your fortune as often as you want. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill is not shared with the skill developer. However it's on public view so anyone can share this. Share this with your friends and family. Learn random moon facts with the zodiac with Mystic Keeper™. If you want a personalized horoscope. Contact him on any social media with the same logo. or any listed as Mystic Keeper™. Alexa will pick 3 different styles. Lucky days or rewarding days, challenging days and bad days. This is simple moon astrology and has 36 different replies for them. You must have understanding of how and when the moon is in all the zodiac signs. If you need a free listing of that will list the current zodiac sign that is in the moon. You can use google or youtube to use and find out information on moon signs in astrology.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
